{"tid":1440540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[整合] 飲品店抵制名單","createTime":"2019-08-10T12:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T12:53:31.000Z","uid":283552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ebde092598a1f3dab0c6461c1fcb50dbed2d7282","tid":1440540,"uid":283552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2OqTYVe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2OqTYVe.jpg&h=2e3128c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除咗逢星期五、日<br />\nBye Buy Day之外<br />\n希望香港人有返d骨氣 平日都罷買/抵制親共商鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n夏天出街大家都會想買杯野飲下<br />\n我知道大家都冇乜記性 (包括我自己)<br />\n但唔想再見到大家遊行完走去排老虎堂個d<br />\n所以決定要整合下d罷買飲品店名單<br />\n<br />\n三大罷飲重點: <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.老虎堂</span> </span>(老細話遊行人士無事生非)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1215175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1215175</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2.幸福堂</span></span> (有見過有comment話老細IG撐警但搵唔返source，股東話罷工當無故曠工)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430022</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3.Crostini</span></span> (老闆炒遊行員工，佔中後講明唔請黃絲)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2363660787054064?s=1347053897&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F178965725523592%2Fposts%2F2363660787054064%3Fs%3D1347053897%26sfns%3Dmo&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=ff8d13cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2363660787054064?s=1347053897&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外跟據「台灣也有一個騰訊」Facebook罷飲名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366585567437682/posts/497281564368081?s=1347053897&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F366585567437682%2Fposts%2F497281564368081%3Fs%3D1347053897%26sfns%3Dmo&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=65a6a902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/366585567437682/posts/497281564368081?s=1347053897&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"456747d6d72756387e62d6360a4e8de57a2e4143","tid":1440540,"uid":283552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:48:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366585567437682/posts/497281564368081?s=1347053897&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F366585567437682%2Fposts%2F497281564368081%3Fs%3D1347053897%26sfns%3Dmo&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=65a6a902\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/366585567437682/posts/497281564368081?s=1347053897&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">【在台之中國飲料店整理名單】<br />\n與迷因刻本 Xylographic Memes合作</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 良辰吉時</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/5eK6R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2F5eK6R&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=559df316\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/5eK6R</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. COCO</span><br />\n-「都可堅決服從與支持國家法規政策，其中當然包括香港地區是中華人民共和國不可分割的一部分。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/9M6aV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2F9M6aV&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=af68d28b\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/9M6aV</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 貢茶</span><br />\n-「堅決支持一國兩制，香港是中國不可分割的一部分」<br />\n<a href=\"https: