xQYn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FjxQYn&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=977edc19\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/jxQYn</a>（KOI：50嵐中區代理商在中國設點名稱）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10. 大苑子</span> <span style=\"color: brown;\">(香港無分店)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/WjA7L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FWjA7L&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=a1ebeb26\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/WjA7L</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">11. 一芳水果茶</span> <span style=\"color: brown;\">(自行判斷)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/z0pE6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2Fz0pE6&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=38686cd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/z0pE6</a><br />\n-有人話香港加盟店係同路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/1097897725/posts/10214635842145229/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F1097897725%2Fposts%2F10214635842145229%2F&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=4037e73f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/1097897725/posts/10214635842145229/</a><br />\n-但有人又話香港店掙咗嘅錢都要分成俾總公司<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420219\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420219</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">12. 迷客夏</span> <span style=\"color: brown;\">(自行判斷)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/qyn6N\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2Fqyn6N&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=a1f8ba8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/qyn6N</a><br />\n-有人話中國嗰個迷客夏唔係台灣迷客夏<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2879957\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2879957&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=9c47c74d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2879957</a><br />\n-又有人話香港嗰間係同路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438749\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438749</a>  (#115 #143)<br />\n-迷客夏最新聲明解釋，因為微信公眾號內容審查緣故，如果要使用使用台灣，就必須加上中國<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/台灣新聞/362327/兩岸角力-政治表態遭陸台網民先後抵制-台多間飲品店急澄清\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F362327%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E9%81%AD%E9%99%B8%E5%8F%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%85%88%E5%BE%8C%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6-%E5%8F%B0%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%93%E9%A3%B2%E5%93%81%E5%BA%97%E6%80%A5%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=caa33ad4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/台灣新聞/362327/兩岸角力-政治表態遭陸台網民先後抵制-台多間飲品店急澄清</a>"},{"pid":"af1ee5947fa0863f2587908288106a28cfe040c4","tid":1440540,"uid":283552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:53:31.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}